---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Resume | Justin Hoffmann">
  <section class="resume">
    <h1>Resume</h1>

    <p class="intro">
      IT Support Technician with experience supporting Microsoft 365, Windows,
      networking, and endpoint management in a Managed Service Provider (MSP)
      environment. Skilled in troubleshooting hardware, software, Microsoft 365,
      and network issues while delivering excellent customer support. Passionate
      about systems administration, virtualization, Linux, automation, and
      infrastructure technologies.
    </p>

    <a
      class="download-btn"
      href="public/images/Justin_Hoffmann_Resume_July2026.pdf"
      target="_blank"
      rel="noopener noreferrer"
    >
      ⬇ Download Resume
    </a>

    <h2>Professional Experience</h2>

    <div class="job">
      <h3>Business Information Solutions</h3>
      <p class="job-title">IT Support Technician | March 2026 – Present</p>

      <ul>
        <li>
          Provide remote and onsite technical support for business clients.
        </li>
        <li>
          Administer Microsoft 365, Microsoft Entra ID, and Exchange Online.
        </li>
        <li>
          Troubleshoot Windows, printers, networking, and endpoint security
          solutions.
        </li>
        <li>
          Configure workstations, onboard users, and resolve hardware and
          software issues.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="job">
      <h3>Harris Business Machines</h3>
      <p class="job-title">
        Service / Network Technician | September 2022 – February 2026
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>
          Configured TCP/IP, DHCP, SMB file sharing, and printer connectivity.
        </li>
        <li>Diagnosed hardware, firmware, software, and networking issues.</li>
        <li>Performed remote support using TeamViewer.</li>
        <li>
          Installed, repaired, and maintained office technology while minimizing
          downtime.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="job">
      <h3>Metric</h3>
      <p class="job-title">Field Supervisor | October 2018 – September 2022</p>

      <p>
        Supervised field operations while providing hardware and software
        technical assistance and improving communication across multiple
        projects.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>Technical Skills</h2>

    <div class="skills">
      <span>Microsoft 365</span>
      <span>Microsoft Entra ID</span>
      <span>Active Directory</span>
      <span>Exchange Online</span>
      <span>Windows Server</span>
      <span>Linux</span>
      <span>PowerShell</span>
      <span>Proxmox VE</span>
      <span>Docker</span>
      <span>TCP/IP</span>
      <span>DHCP</span>
      <span>DNS</span>
      <span>VPN</span>
      <span>NinjaOne</span>
      <span>SentinelOne</span>
      <span>Huntress</span>
      <span>Guardz</span>
      <span>Barracuda</span>
    </div>

    <h2>Certifications</h2>

    <ul class="certifications">
      <li>CompTIA A+</li>
      <li>3CX VoIP Certified Technician</li>
      <li>Canon Full-Line Certified Technician</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="cta">
      <h2>Projects</h2>

      <p>
        Want to see these technologies in action? Explore my home lab and
        technical projects where I document the solutions I've built and the
        skills I've developed.
      </p>

      <a href="/projects" class="projects-button"> View My Projects → </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .resume {
    max-width: 850px;
    margin: 80px auto;
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .resume h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .resume h2 {
    margin-top: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #cbd5e1;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .download-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.6rem;
    background: #2563eb;
    color: white;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: background 0.2s ease;
  }

  .download-btn:hover {
    background: #1d4ed8;
  }

  .job {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .job h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .job-title {
    color: #94a3b8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .job ul {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
  }

  .job li {
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .skills {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }

  .skills span {
    background: #1e293b;
    border: 1px solid #334155;
    padding: 0.6rem 1rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #f8fafc;
  }

  .certifications {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
  }

  .certifications li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .cta {
    margin-top: 4rem;
    text-align: center;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid #334155;
  }

  .projects-button {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding: 0.85rem 1.6rem;
    border: 1px solid #2563eb;
    border-radius: 8px;
    color: #60a5fa;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
  }

  .projects-button:hover {
    background: #2563eb;
    color: white;
  }
</style>
